-- Brioni Names General Manager Bianchini as Interim Head of Fashion Company
-- Andrew Roberts
-- 2010-07-07T06:08:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/brioni-names-general-manager-bianchini-as-interim-head-of-fashion-company.html

          
          
             Brioni Roman Style SpA  said general
manager  Antonio Bianchini  will handle the day-to-day running of
the Italian suitmaker until it appoints a new chief executive
officer.  
 Andrea Perrone , the 40 year-old grandson of Brioni co-
founder  Gaetano Savini , resigned as CEO of the Penne, Italy-
based company, a spokeswoman said yesterday.  
 Perrone resigned July 5 for personal reasons, Brioni said
in a statement.  
